        <h2>Project Overview</h2>
        <p>This project involved developing an intuitive PowerApps application for consultants at the Clatterbridge Cancer Trust.</p>
        <h3>Features:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Apps gallery with icons, names, and descriptions</li>
            <li>Favourite, request access, and run action buttons</li>
            <li>Search bar for quick app access</li>
            <li>Personalized request access functionality with confirmation pop-ups</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Technologies Used:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Microsoft PowerApps</li>
            <li>Power Automate</li>
        </ul>
